Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.48,0:00:53.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,常軌を逸した狂気のゲーム
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.66,0:00:53.10,default,,0,0,0,,The extraordinary game\Nof insanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.75,0:00:59.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,３種類 10枚のカードを使って
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.75,0:00:59.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,行われるゲーム｢Ｅカード｣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.77,0:00:58.79,default,,0,0,0,,A game using ten cards of\Nthree different types, E-Card.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.10,0:01:01.10,default,,0,0,0,,Win and get great fortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.13,0:01:03.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝てば大金を手に
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.13,0:01:03.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,負ければ その代償として
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.10,0:01:05.34,default,,0,0,0,,If he loses, he will lose his sense\Nof hearing in his left ear.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.10,0:01:06.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,左耳の聴力を失う
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.03,0:01:09.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジは初戦 ２戦と
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.03,0:01:09.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,連続で勝ちを拾い
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.14,0:01:11.25,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji won two games in a row\Nand gained two million!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.67,0:01:11.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,200万を得る
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.61,0:01:15.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ふっふっ… 感じる 感じる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.89,0:01:15.05,default,,0,0,0,,I can finally feel it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.26,0:01:18.25,default,,0,0,0,,Finally the feeling is\N passed on to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.28,0:01:19.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ようやく気配が届いてきた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.01,0:01:22.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ君の心の波動が
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.02,0:01:21.79,default,,0,0,0,,The vibrations of your heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.02,0:01:26.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今 少しずつ　ふっふっふっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.17,0:01:23.92,default,,0,0,0,,little by little...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.72,0:01:29.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,では ３戦目だ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.73,0:01:28.93,default,,0,0,0,,Now, let's proceed\Nto the third match.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.87,0:01:32.81,kaiji-main-top,,0,0,0,,Adversity
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.46,0:01:36.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何をわけの分からないことを
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.56,0:01:36.44,default,,0,0,0,,What exactly is he talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.86,0:01:39.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,とんだ負け惜しみ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.94,0:01:38.67,default,,0,0,0,,He is such a sore loser.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.10,0:01:40.68,default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing but a bluff!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.17,0:01:41.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こけおどしに決まってる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.77,0:01:46.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,オープン
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.78,0:01:45.15,default,,0,0,0,,Open!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.33,0:01:49.51,default,,0,0,0,,Just like in the first two rounds,\Nboth players chose...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.47,0:01:51.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１～２戦目と同じく
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.47,0:01:51.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１枚目は両者ともに市民を選択
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.51,0:01:51.67,default,,0,0,0,,...Citizen as their first card.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.68,0:02:00.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この３戦目の後 今度は俺が奴隷側
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.68,0:02:00.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝ちにくくなる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.70,0:01:58.11,default,,0,0,0,,After this third round,  I'll have\Nto play on the Slave side.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.40,0:01:59.39,default,,0,0,0,,It will be harder to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.49,0:02:03.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もうひとつ ここで勝っておきたい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.64,0:02:02.78,default,,0,0,0,,I want to win again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.86,0:02:07.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうする？もう１回
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.86,0:02:07.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここで皇帝を通しに行くか？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.92,0:02:04.82,default,,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.18,0:02:07.62,default,,0,0,0,,Shall I use the Emperor\None more time?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.63,0:02:12.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まさか３回連続とは思うまい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.72,0:02:12.14,default,,0,0,0,,He wouldn't expect\Nthree Emperors in a row.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.12,0:02:19.22,default,,0,0,0,,I can finally feel it,\Nthe vibrations of your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.17,0:02:17.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,感じる 感じる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.50,0:02:20.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,心の波動
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.14,0:02:24.00,default,,0,0,0,,For sure, that was\Ndefinitely just a bluff!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.17,0:02:25.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こけおどしだ あんなもの
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.17,0:02:25.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハッタリなんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.41,0:02:27.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,感じる 感じる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.43,0:02:27.39,default,,0,0,0,,I can finally feel it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.84,0:02:28.94,default,,0,0,0,,Darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.85,0:02:30.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,くそっ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.13,0:02:38.10,default,,0,0,0,,Come on! Slave!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.22,0:02:38.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,来い　奴隷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.16,0:02:40.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,奴隷で自爆しろ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.28,0:02:39.87,default,,0,0,0,,Darn it! Use the Slave\Nand blow yourself up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.84,0:02:52.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝負は初めて３枚目に突入
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.92,0:02:52.11,default,,0,0,0,,They played the third card\Nfor the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.61,0:02:56.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうする？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.61,0:02:56.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう一度 市民で行くか？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.65,0:02:55.85,default,,0,0,0,,What should I do?\NPlay the Citizen once more?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.41,0:03:00.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや… ここで市民を選択して
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.41,0:03:00.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,また引き分けになると
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.48,0:02:57.32,default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.32,0:03:00.12,default,,0,0,0,,If Citizen is used here,\Nthe game will be a draw.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.28,0:03:04.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,残り２枚　勝率は５分５分
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.34,0:03:03.36,default,,0,0,0,,The probability\Nwill then be 50-50.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.51,0:03:05.95,default,,0,0,0,,I'll settle this here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.55,0:03:07.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここで勝負だ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.33,0:03:08.86,default,,0,0,0,,Come on! Citizen!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.35,0:03:11.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,来い　市民！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.35,0:03:11.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,皇帝でねじ伏せてやる
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.24,0:03:10.95,default,,0,0,0,,I'll crush you with the Emperor!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.12,0:03:14.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,来い　来い　市民
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.15,0:03:13.80,default,,0,0,0,,Come on! Citizen!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.96,0:03:20.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなに強く念じられては
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.96,0:03:20.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,丸聞こえだ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.05,0:03:20.54,default,,0,0,0,,Don't stress yourself\Nby thinking too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.93,0:03:24.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はっきりと聞こえてきたぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.07,0:03:22.99,default,,0,0,0,,I can hear you clearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.04,0:03:26.54,default,,0,0,0,,"Come on, Citizen!" you said.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.07,0:03:28.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,｢来い 市民！｣ とな
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.83,0:03:27.72,default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.04,0:03:32.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,つまりカイジ君のカードは皇帝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.29,0:03:30.55,default,,0,0,0,,Which means, your card is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.75,0:03:32.55,default,,0,0,0,,Emperor!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.65,0:03:45.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バカな　こいつ 本当に
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.65,0:03:45.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺の思ってたことを…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.76,0:03:41.76,default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.28,0:03:44.73,default,,0,0,0,,Could he really hear\Nwhat I was thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.84,0:03:47.97,default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me he's psychic?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.86,0:03:48.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まさか読心術？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.76,0:03:52.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ふふふ… さあ オープンしたまえ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.92,0:03:51.47,default,,0,0,0,,Now, show me your card.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.53,0:03:56.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ　初めての敗北
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.54,0:03:56.21,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji loses for the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.41,0:04:03.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,では参ろうか さっそく
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.58,0:04:02.41,default,,0,0,0,,Now, let's get started.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.10,0:04:04.50,default,,0,0,0,,10mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.18,0:04:05.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,10ミリだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.92,0:04:20.93,default,,0,0,0,,Drill, drill, drill...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.72,0:04:26.94,default,,0,0,0,,The sound is\Ninaudible from here,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.97,0:04:27.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,外に漏れる音はわずか
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.42,0:04:30.44,default,,0,0,0,,but for you,\Nit's tearing you up inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.25,0:04:49.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しばらくは残響で
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.25,0:04:49.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,顔も上げられまい
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.28,0:04:48.07,default,,0,0,0,,You won't be able to\Nlift your head up with that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.07,0:04:49.75,default,,0,0,0,,...deafening sound\Nreverberating in your ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.62,0:04:52.96,default,,0,0,0,,Tonegawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.63,0:04:56.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,利根川　ほどほどにな
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.35,0:04:56.03,default,,0,0,0,,Bring it down a notch.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.33,0:05:00.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,相手の混乱を誘う話術も面白いが
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.36,0:05:00.16,default,,0,0,0,,Although it's interesting to\Nwear your opponent down,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.20,0:05:03.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,度が過ぎて
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.20,0:05:03.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ君が恐れるあまり
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.36,0:05:02.86,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji might lose\Nall his will to fight...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.86,0:05:06.01,default,,0,0,0,,...if you push him\Nover the edge.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.10,0:05:06.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,戦意喪失しては興を失う
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.31,0:05:08.47,default,,0,0,0,,Director, don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.34,0:05:08.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,会長　ご安心を
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.94,0:05:12.38,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji's not the way he seems.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.94,0:05:12.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こう見えてカイジ君は
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.94,0:05:12.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なかなかの つわものでして
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.78,0:05:16.66,default,,0,0,0,,I'm certain that he\Ncan see right through this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.78,0:05:17.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この程度のことは
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.78,0:05:17.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっさりと見破ってくれます
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.26,0:05:20.02,default,,0,0,0,,See right through it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.28,0:05:20.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,見破る？話術？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.19,0:05:22.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺を混乱させるだと？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.23,0:05:22.02,default,,0,0,0,,To confuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.99,0:05:28.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハメやがったな 利根川
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.12,0:05:28.03,default,,0,0,0,,You tricked me, Tonegawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.70,0:05:31.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前は俺の心が
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.70,0:05:31.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,読めたわけじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.74,0:05:31.53,default,,0,0,0,,You can't read my mind at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.73,0:05:36.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あれは俺の考えを言い当てたふり
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.73,0:05:36.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カマをかけたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.90,0:05:34.53,default,,0,0,0,,You were just pretending\Nto be able to!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.76,0:05:36.04,default,,0,0,0,,It was just a trick!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.30,0:05:38.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ほう…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.30,0:05:38.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああいう場合
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.83,0:05:41.88,default,,0,0,0,,It's natural to want your\Nopponent to play a certain card.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.74,0:05:42.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,相手の出してほしいカードを
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.74,0:05:42.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,念じるのは当たり前だ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.14,0:05:45.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺が念じるカードは
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.14,0:05:45.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,市民か奴隷のどちらか
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.16,0:05:45.20,default,,0,0,0,,The card I was hoping\Nhas a 50% chance...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.58,0:05:47.58,default,,0,0,0,,...of being either\Na Citizen or Slave!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.65,0:05:48.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,確率は50パーセント
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.14,0:05:51.32,default,,0,0,0,,"Come on", is just a\Ncommonly used phrase!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.18,0:05:51.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,｢来い｣という呼びかけも
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.18,0:05:51.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,言ってみりゃ常套句
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.72,0:05:55.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなに強く念じられては
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.72,0:05:55.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,丸聞こえだ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.76,0:05:55.00,default,,0,0,0,,Don't stress yourself up\N by thinking too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.59,0:05:58.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はっきりと聞こえてきたぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.70,0:05:57.53,default,,0,0,0,,I can hear you clearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.06,0:06:00.56,default,,0,0,0,,"Come on, Citizen!" you said.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.13,0:06:01.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,｢来い 市民！｣ とな
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.16,0:06:04.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺の動揺を見て
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.16,0:06:04.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,図星と分かったところで
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.32,0:06:04.56,default,,0,0,0,,You figured out my card when\Nyou saw that I was agitated.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.73,0:06:10.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,つまりカイジ君のカードは皇帝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.75,0:06:07.07,default,,0,0,0,,Which means, your card is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.06,0:06:09.07,default,,0,0,0,,Emperor!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.54,0:06:14.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,自分のカードを選択した
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.56,0:06:12.65,default,,0,0,0,,Then you chose your card!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.41,0:06:16.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,本当に俺の心が読めてたなら
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.55,0:06:19.41,default,,0,0,0,,If you're truly psychic,\Nthen show your card before mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.78,0:06:20.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,最初に自分のカードを出せば
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.78,0:06:20.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いいはずだ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.78,0:06:23.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さすがはカイジ君
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.97,0:06:22.38,default,,0,0,0,,As I expected of Kaiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.55,0:06:27.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが50点だ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.57,0:06:25.15,default,,0,0,0,,But you are only half right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.00,0:06:29.11,default,,0,0,0,,"Please", "I  beg of you"...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.02,0:06:29.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,｢お願い｣｢頼む｣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.56,0:06:31.64,default,,0,0,0,,"Come here", "Come on".
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.56,0:06:32.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,｢来てくれ｣｢来い｣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.30,0:06:36.18,default,,0,0,0,,Indeed, these are\Ncommonly used phrases...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.33,0:06:36.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,確かにあの状況で
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.33,0:06:36.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,相手に出してほしいカードを
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.10,0:06:39.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,念じる時に使う言葉としては
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.10,0:06:39.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一般的だ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.18,0:06:38.96,default,,0,0,0,,...in hoping that your opponent\Nplays the card you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.54,0:06:42.29,default,,0,0,0,,And when you're winning\Nfor 90% of the time,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.57,0:06:42.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ましてや連勝している
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.57,0:06:42.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの場面では
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.29,0:06:45.65,default,,0,0,0,,you are more likely\Nto say "Come on".
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.30,0:06:46.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,最も積極的な言葉 ｢来い｣を使う
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.11,0:06:48.63,default,,0,0,0,,That was exactly\Nwhat you were thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.14,0:06:48.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その点は君の想像どおりだ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.63,0:06:49.94,default,,0,0,0,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.64,0:06:51.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,貴様！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.64,0:06:51.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ただ…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.14,0:06:51.14,default,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.34,0:06:54.94,default,,0,0,0,,You were wrong to say that\NI guessed it was a Citizen card.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.34,0:06:55.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カードを市民と言い当てた点は
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.34,0:06:55.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まるでダメだ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.94,0:06:55.95,default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.05,0:06:58.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.05,0:06:58.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,君は私が５割の確率で
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.78,0:07:01.67,default,,0,0,0,,You assumed that I\Nchose the card at random.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.92,0:07:01.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,適当に選んだと
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.92,0:07:01.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,考えているようだが
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.82,0:07:05.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんな安っぽいもんじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.86,0:07:03.69,default,,0,0,0,,But it's not that simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.26,0:07:08.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私は本当に感じられるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.28,0:07:08.02,default,,0,0,0,,I can really feel it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.16,0:07:13.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,人の心の震え どのカードを
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.16,0:07:13.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,出そうとしているのか
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.34,0:07:10.33,default,,0,0,0,,The beating of hearts...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.33,0:07:12.96,default,,0,0,0,,...and which card\Nthey have chosen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.73,0:07:16.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ふざけるな　じゃあ何か？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.74,0:07:14.98,default,,0,0,0,,That's a lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.23,0:07:18.40,default,,0,0,0,,What then? Can you see\Nright through my soul?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.10,0:07:18.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,心が透けて見えるとでも
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.10,0:07:18.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,言うのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.74,0:07:20.74,default,,0,0,0,,Are you a mind reader?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.74,0:07:21.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前は超能力者だと
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.00,0:07:24.62,default,,0,0,0,,Of course,\NI'm not a mind reader.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.01,0:07:24.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もちろん私は
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.01,0:07:24.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,超能力者などではない
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.78,0:07:28.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが それに近いことはできる
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.78,0:07:28.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何だと？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.80,0:07:26.97,default,,0,0,0,,But I can do something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.97,0:07:27.74,default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.64,0:07:30.25,default,,0,0,0,,It's due to experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.65,0:07:30.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,経験によってな
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.92,0:07:35.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私はそれこそ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.92,0:07:35.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,10年20年と見続けてきた
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.96,0:07:32.75,default,,0,0,0,,In the past 20 years,\NI have witnessed...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.75,0:07:34.72,default,,0,0,0,,...many deaths\Ncaused by gambling.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.09,0:07:38.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,生き死にに関わる人間の姿をな
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.13,0:07:38.18,default,,0,0,0,,People struggling with debts\Nand living at their wits end.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.76,0:07:43.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,人生のどん詰まりで
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.76,0:07:43.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,彼らが何を考え 何を望むか
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.78,0:07:43.61,default,,0,0,0,,I've seen what these people\Nhope and wish for...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.63,0:07:49.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その心の揺れが 体のどの部分に
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.63,0:07:49.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,反応として現れるかを見てきた
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.83,0:07:49.13,default,,0,0,0,,...and the constant\Ntrembling of their hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.50,0:07:51.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だから このＥカードも
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.61,0:07:51.75,default,,0,0,0,,That's why\Nin this game of E-Card,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.64,0:07:55.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１～２回見ただけで
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.64,0:07:55.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,相手がどのタイプに属する人間か
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.75,0:07:55.64,default,,0,0,0,,I have an uncanny ability\Nto judge a player...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.84,0:07:58.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おおよそ見当がついてしまう
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.88,0:07:58.32,default,,0,0,0,,...after a round or two.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.74,0:08:00.80,default,,0,0,0,,You are no exception.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.75,0:08:00.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,君も例外ではない
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.98,0:08:03.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その性質や癖
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.01,0:08:04.51,default,,0,0,0,,With your temperament\Nand habits,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.25,0:08:08.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今やすでに この手の中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.96,0:08:06.52,default,,0,0,0,,you're like an open book.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.12,0:08:12.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,残りの９戦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.12,0:08:12.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,君はこの中でもがくだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.27,0:08:12.55,default,,0,0,0,,In the remaining nine rounds,\Nyou will surely lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.72,0:08:14.25,default,,0,0,0,,Give me a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.86,0:08:18.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いい加減にしろ　１勝しただけで
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.86,0:08:18.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,得意げにハッタリかましやがって
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.25,0:08:17.06,default,,0,0,0,,Don't be so cocky!\NYou've only won one game!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.97,0:08:20.56,default,,0,0,0,,You'll know when we play.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.97,0:08:21.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やれば分かる
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.57,0:08:23.56,default,,0,0,0,,Now it's your turn to\Nplay the Slave side.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.57,0:08:23.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今度は君が奴隷側だ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.07,0:08:28.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺の考えが読めるだと？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.20,0:08:29.86,default,,0,0,0,,He read my thoughts!\NBut that's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.48,0:08:30.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなこと…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.57,0:08:33.69,default,,0,0,0,,What's the problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.68,0:08:35.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうした？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.58,0:08:39.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前のくだらないハッタリで
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.58,0:08:39.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ケチがついた
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.59,0:08:38.43,default,,0,0,0,,Your stupid trick\Nruined my mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.52,0:08:42.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,顔でも洗ってくる
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.58,0:08:41.15,default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to wash my face.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.18,0:09:06.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,人の心を読むなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.18,0:09:06.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,できっこねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.20,0:09:06.61,default,,0,0,0,,There's no way\Nhe can read minds!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.85,0:09:14.51,default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.85,0:09:15.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,できっこねえんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.55,0:09:21.85,default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.56,0:09:22.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,できっこねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.01,0:09:40.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうだった？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.03,0:09:38.42,default,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.35,0:09:44.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カードに印など
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.35,0:09:44.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ついてなかったろう？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.38,0:09:42.57,default,,0,0,0,,There are no marks\Non the cards, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.25,0:09:47.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなこと やりはせんよ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.33,0:09:46.08,default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't do such a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.75,0:09:52.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなことをすれば バレた時に
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.75,0:09:52.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,逆に利用されかねない
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.78,0:09:51.48,default,,0,0,0,,I doubt I'd ever stoop so low\Njust to win a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.01,0:09:57.29,default,,0,0,0,,To us, this game is purely\Nfor recreation's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.06,0:09:55.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,第一 君はともかく
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.06,0:09:55.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,我々にしてみれば
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.36,0:09:58.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今回のゲームは遊び
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.23,0:10:02.11,default,,0,0,0,,I'm just enjoying the\Npsychological battle with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.26,0:10:02.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,純粋にカイジ君との心理戦を
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.26,0:10:02.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,楽しもうとしているだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.27,0:10:06.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,印など無用だ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.42,0:10:03.90,default,,0,0,0,,There's no need to mark them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.44,0:10:10.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,むしろ君が印をつけていないか…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.44,0:10:10.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.47,0:10:10.14,default,,0,0,0,,Rather, we should be\Nkeeping an eye on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.46,0:10:10.14,kaiji-main-top,,0,0,0,,Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.14,0:10:13.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こちらが警戒しなければ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.14,0:10:13.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いけないくらいだ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.14,0:10:13.10,default,,0,0,0,,Just to be safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.22,0:10:21.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,では再開するとしよう
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.23,0:10:21.41,default,,0,0,0,,Let's get on with the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.93,0:10:35.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さて ベットは？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.13,0:10:33.36,default,,0,0,0,,Now, what's your bet?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.13,0:10:37.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,変わらず10か？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.22,0:10:36.70,default,,0,0,0,,10 as usual?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.07,0:10:41.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,2000万に届くためには そう簡単に
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.07,0:10:41.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,距離は減らせないだろうからな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.09,0:10:41.36,default,,0,0,0,,To get 20 million, you can't\Nreduce the amount too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.36,0:10:42.46,default,,0,0,0,,Darn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.47,0:10:43.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ふざけろ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.29,0:10:45.41,default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'll win three in a row.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.41,0:10:45.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,３連勝したのなら ともかく
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.64,0:10:49.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今度は勝ちの薄い奴隷側で
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.64,0:10:49.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,10ミリも張れるわけない
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.70,0:10:49.17,default,,0,0,0,,This time, I'm playing on the\NSlave side. I won't bet 10mm!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.41,0:10:51.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ほう
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.68,0:10:56.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それは すばらしい
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.68,0:10:56.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何だと？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.82,0:10:55.60,default,,0,0,0,,That's wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.60,0:10:56.55,default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.99,0:10:59.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さっき会長と次にカイジ君が
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.08,0:11:01.68,default,,0,0,0,,We were just discussing\Nhow much you would wager.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.22,0:11:01.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どれだけ張ってくるか
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.22,0:11:01.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,という話になってね
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.68,0:11:02.83,default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.43,0:11:05.89,default,,0,0,0,,We had an agreement.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.53,0:11:06.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,互いに意見が一致したところだ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.53,0:11:10.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここで10張るようなヤツは
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.53,0:11:10.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,話にならんとな
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.71,0:11:10.07,default,,0,0,0,,Anyone who bets 10\Nat this point is worthless.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.83,0:11:13.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなやからは
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.83,0:11:13.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ただの怖いもの知らず
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.92,0:11:15.30,default,,0,0,0,,Only fools would bet\Nso foolishly and carelessly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.74,0:11:15.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,引くべきところは引く
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.67,0:11:20.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それが我々の言うところの
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.67,0:11:20.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,つわものだ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.88,0:11:19.30,default,,0,0,0,,You are indeed as good\Nas we said.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.38,0:11:22.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,では いくら張る？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.44,0:11:22.04,default,,0,0,0,,So what will your wager be?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.95,0:11:28.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,２だ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.98,0:11:26.78,default,,0,0,0,,2.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.79,0:11:31.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,10から２か
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.84,0:11:30.43,default,,0,0,0,,From 10 to 2?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.51,0:11:32.79,default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.52,0:11:35.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,黙れ　８や５は張れとでも
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.52,0:11:35.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,言いたいんだろうが 今は…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.79,0:11:35.52,default,,0,0,0,,You wanted me to place\Na higher bet, but now...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.46,0:11:37.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,逆だ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.67,0:11:36.58,default,,0,0,0,,It's opposite!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.93,0:11:42.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,誠のつわものならば
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.93,0:11:42.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここは１まで落とす
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.98,0:11:41.19,default,,0,0,0,,At this stage, a real fighter\Nwould reduce it to 1.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.53,0:11:46.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝算もなく
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.53,0:11:46.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,流れが相手に傾いている今
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.59,0:11:46.05,default,,0,0,0,,With no guarantee of winning and\Nthe tide in the opponent's hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.05,0:11:47.93,default,,0,0,0,,you should place\Nyour bet at 1.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.07,0:11:48.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,張りは限界まで落とすべき
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.37,0:11:51.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なのに君は２を張るという
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.46,0:11:51.17,default,,0,0,0,,Despite that, you bet 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.78,0:11:55.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この余分な１は
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.78,0:11:55.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ君の心のぜい肉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.90,0:11:56.74,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji, the additional 1mm\Nis merely your foolish pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.45,0:11:58.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,見えというものだ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.28,0:12:03.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,死ぬぞ　その見えが
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.28,0:12:03.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あとあとカイジ君の首を絞める
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.32,0:11:59.48,default,,0,0,0,,You will falter.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.87,0:12:03.54,default,,0,0,0,,That pride of yours will\Nbe your downfall.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.99,0:12:08.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうする？今なら変更を認めよう
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.08,0:12:07.18,default,,0,0,0,,What will you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.32,0:12:09.05,default,,0,0,0,,You're still allowed\Nto make changes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.93,0:12:10.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,男がいったん口にした張りを
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.05,0:12:13.08,default,,0,0,0,,Once a man places his bet,\Nthe decision is final!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.93,0:12:14.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうヒョイヒョイ変えられるか
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.93,0:12:14.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ほっとけ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.08,0:12:14.26,default,,0,0,0,,Let it be!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.06,0:12:17.51,default,,0,0,0,,- Drill, drill, drill...\N- I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.33,0:12:21.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうか　別にこちらはかまわんよ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.88,0:12:20.00,default,,0,0,0,,It makes no difference to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.00,0:12:20.80,default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.91,0:12:28.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ　奴隷側となっての４戦目
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.94,0:12:27.90,default,,0,0,0,,The fourth game, with\NKaiji on the Slave side...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.18,0:12:32.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,皇帝側の利根川に続いて
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.18,0:12:32.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カードの選択
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.26,0:12:30.40,default,,0,0,0,,...and Tonegawa\Non the Emperor side.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.40,0:12:31.90,default,,0,0,0,,He chooses his card.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.05,0:12:34.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここで勝てば流れを変えられる
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.24,0:12:34.88,default,,0,0,0,,If he wins here,\Nthe flow will change.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.88,0:12:39.41,default,,0,0,0,,But there's a thought\Nthat Kaiji can't shake off.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.89,0:12:37.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが カイジの心には
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.12,0:12:40.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,拭いきれない考えが生じている
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.02,0:12:43.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハッタリだと分かっていながらも
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.02,0:12:43.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ひょっとすると
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.09,0:12:43.65,default,,0,0,0,,Even if he knows it's a bluff,\Nthere might be a chance...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.89,0:12:47.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,本当に心を
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.89,0:12:47.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,見抜かれているのではないかと
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.06,0:12:47.25,default,,0,0,0,,...that his mind is\Nindeed being read.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.76,0:12:51.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや そう考えさせることが
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.76,0:12:51.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ヤツの手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.90,0:12:51.44,default,,0,0,0,,No, it's just a trick he's using.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.64,0:12:53.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この呪縛 解かなきゃダメだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.68,0:12:53.91,default,,0,0,0,,I must break out of this trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.87,0:12:56.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そのためには勝つしかない
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.91,0:12:55.66,default,,0,0,0,,To do that, I have to win!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.30,0:13:01.79,default,,0,0,0,,If I win this round,\NTonegawa's tactics will fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.31,0:13:00.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺が勝てば 利根川の
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.31,0:13:00.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの大仰な言葉も すべてごたく
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.31,0:13:03.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,魔法は解ける
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.58,0:13:06.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,待てよ　てことは
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.58,0:13:06.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,負けられないのは
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.63,0:13:04.71,default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.71,0:13:07.67,default,,0,0,0,,Tonegawa has much more\Nto lose than I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.42,0:13:08.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺よりむしろ利根川
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.85,0:13:12.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,有利なはずの皇帝で
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.85,0:13:12.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ましてや あの会長とやらの前で
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.91,0:13:10.53,default,,0,0,0,,With Emperor\Nas the advantage...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.53,0:13:15.48,default,,0,0,0,,...and losing to me\Nin front of the Director,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.72,0:13:15.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺みたいな小物相手に
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.72,0:13:15.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,負けるなんて醜態
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.39,0:13:17.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,許されるはずがない
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.48,0:13:17.28,default,,0,0,0,,they'd never forgive him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.96,0:13:21.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,利根川は今
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.96,0:13:21.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺以上に勝ちたいはずなんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.04,0:13:21.57,default,,0,0,0,,Tonegawa is under more\Npressure to win than I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.83,0:13:25.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,とすれば ヤツのカードは何だ？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.83,0:13:25.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,皇帝か？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.89,0:13:24.85,default,,0,0,0,,Which card is he holding?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.85,0:13:26.01,default,,0,0,0,,Emperor?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.07,0:13:31.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや 違う
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.07,0:13:31.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ヤツは今 あおることで
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.16,0:13:29.36,default,,0,0,0,,No, that's not right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.89,0:13:33.40,default,,0,0,0,,He is now trying\Nto read my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.41,0:13:34.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺を一種の興奮状態に導き
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.04,0:13:38.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１枚目から奴隷で
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.04,0:13:38.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝負を仕掛ける状況を作ったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.10,0:13:37.59,default,,0,0,0,,Dealing a Slave card as your\Nfirst hand would be risking it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.55,0:13:42.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なら その危険な１枚目に
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.55,0:13:42.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,皇帝を出してくるはずはない
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.70,0:13:42.41,default,,0,0,0,,Even so, he would not place\NEmperor as his very first card.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.82,0:13:50.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１枚目はリスクを避けて… 市民
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.72,0:13:47.78,default,,0,0,0,,The first card would be\Nto avoid risk.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.38,0:13:49.30,default,,0,0,0,,Citizen!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.63,0:13:53.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,オープン
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.84,0:13:51.78,default,,0,0,0,,Open!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.90,0:14:00.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,思ったとおり　もし今
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.90,0:14:00.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,皇帝を出していたら利根川の勝ち
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.98,0:13:57.49,default,,0,0,0,,As I expected!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.49,0:14:00.29,default,,0,0,0,,If Tonegawa placed an\NEmperor then, he'd win.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.74,0:14:02.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それが できなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.74,0:14:02.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ということは
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.80,0:14:05.19,default,,0,0,0,,This shows that he can't\Npredict the cards at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.67,0:14:05.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カードを読み切ってなど
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.67,0:14:05.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いないということ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.58,0:14:09.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,つまり 貴様お得意の話術
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.59,0:14:10.70,default,,0,0,0,,In other words,\Nall that talk was just a lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.55,0:14:12.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハッタリ　勝機はある
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.15,0:14:12.54,default,,0,0,0,,There is a winning chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.88,0:14:15.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,２枚目のカードはカイジから
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.94,0:14:15.44,default,,0,0,0,,The second card\Nstarts with Kaiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.62,0:14:17.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここが最初のヤマ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.70,0:14:17.50,default,,0,0,0,,This is the first obstacle.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.50,0:14:22.95,default,,0,0,0,,For either side, it is difficult\Nto deal a major card...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.55,0:14:20.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,基本的に皇帝側も奴隷側も
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.26,0:14:22.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,自分が先にカードを提出する時
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.86,0:14:27.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝敗の鍵となる皇帝や奴隷は
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.86,0:14:27.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,出しにくい
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.95,0:14:26.50,default,,0,0,0,,...like Emperor or Slave\Nat this point.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.33,0:14:31.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,先にカードを決した側には
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.33,0:14:31.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,心理的な圧迫がある
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.40,0:14:31.40,default,,0,0,0,,For the one who has to go first,\Nthe pressure mounts.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.74,0:14:35.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,顔色からカードを
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.74,0:14:35.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,察知されることもありうる
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.79,0:14:35.09,default,,0,0,0,,From his expression,\Nit'd possible to predict his card.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.21,0:14:40.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その状況下で鍵となるカードを
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.21,0:14:40.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,出すことは避ける
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.30,0:14:39.59,default,,0,0,0,,In this situation, one has to\Navoid playing the decisive card.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.04,0:14:43.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,特に皇帝側は
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.04,0:14:43.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,市民だけ出していれば
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.13,0:14:43.29,default,,0,0,0,,On the Emperor side,\Nif you play the Citizen...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.29,0:14:46.57,default,,0,0,0,,...and the opponent\Nplays a Slave,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.41,0:14:46.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,相手が奴隷を出して
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.41,0:14:46.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,自滅する確率が高く
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.35,0:14:49.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,無理に勝負に行く必要はない
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.57,0:14:48.60,default,,0,0,0,,chances are that\Nhe would be defeated.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.09,0:14:53.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,先出しの１枚目と３枚目は
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.09,0:14:53.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,皇帝を出したくない
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.13,0:14:51.38,default,,0,0,0,,He would avoid\Ndealing the Emperor...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.38,0:14:52.91,default,,0,0,0,,...for the first and third cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.06,0:14:55.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ってことは 逆に考えれば…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.27,0:14:55.11,default,,0,0,0,,In other words...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.96,0:15:00.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こんな序盤でもう長考か？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.89,0:14:57.83,default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.83,0:15:00.11,default,,0,0,0,,I see that someone is\Nthinking way too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.30,0:15:05.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,下手な考え 何とやら
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.38,0:15:08.15,default,,0,0,0,,Thinking too much might\Njust be your downfall.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.54,0:15:07.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これでは先が思いやられるな
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.77,0:15:14.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここから先の修羅場が
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.86,0:15:12.99,default,,0,0,0,,And the gates of doom await.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.13,0:15:34.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さて カイジ君が
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.13,0:15:34.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,じっくり考えたカード
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.24,0:15:33.15,default,,0,0,0,,The card that you pondered\Nso carefully over...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.00,0:15:37.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何が来たか
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.20,0:15:35.65,default,,0,0,0,,What would it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.37,0:15:40.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これは難しいぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.52,0:15:39.65,default,,0,0,0,,This is pretty hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.57,0:15:45.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,２枚目だ　利根川が
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.57,0:15:45.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,皇帝を通すとしたら２枚目だ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.71,0:15:42.04,default,,0,0,0,,The second card!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.36,0:15:44.27,default,,0,0,0,,If Tonegawa wants\Nto deal the Emperor,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.27,0:15:45.16,default,,0,0,0,,it'd be the second card!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.91,0:15:49.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,皇帝側からすれば
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.91,0:15:49.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,後出しの２枚目と４枚目
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.94,0:15:47.57,default,,0,0,0,,From the Emperor side,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.57,0:15:49.66,default,,0,0,0,,one must place it on\Nthe second or fourth card.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.61,0:15:53.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,このどちらかで
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.61,0:15:53.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝負のカードを出す
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.66,0:15:52.25,default,,0,0,0,,This way,\None can aim for victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.08,0:15:57.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが４枚目で勝負となると
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.08,0:15:57.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝率は５割
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.13,0:15:57.07,default,,0,0,0,,But by the fourth card,\Nchances would be 50-50.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.62,0:16:00.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それは避けたいはずだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.67,0:15:59.67,default,,0,0,0,,He ought to\Nwant to avoid that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.19,0:16:06.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ならば ２枚目…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.19,0:16:06.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,２枚目に出してくるはずだ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.28,0:16:01.45,default,,0,0,0,,In other words...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.75,0:16:05.68,default,,0,0,0,,The second card!\NThe second card has to be it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.66,0:16:10.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,難しいが まあ… これか
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.74,0:16:09.18,default,,0,0,0,,It might be hard, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.67,0:16:10.76,default,,0,0,0,,This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.28,0:16:23.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,市民！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.49,0:16:22.66,default,,0,0,0,,Citizen?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.58,0:16:31.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,たわいもない　こちらが
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.58,0:16:31.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,仕掛けずとも自ら転んでくれる
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.70,0:16:27.94,default,,0,0,0,,How foolish.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.94,0:16:31.17,default,,0,0,0,,I don't have to do anything\Nand yet you've faltered.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.78,0:16:57.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ君　援軍だ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.78,0:16:57.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,援軍？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.87,0:16:55.68,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji, you have reinforcements.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.09,0:16:56.83,default,,0,0,0,,Reinforcements?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.85,0:17:03.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何の力にもならぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.85,0:17:03.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,クズのような援軍だがな
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.01,0:17:02.83,default,,0,0,0,,However, reinforcements with\Nno value or use whatsoever.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.46,0:17:10.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さて 続けようか
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.53,0:17:10.17,default,,0,0,0,,Now, shall we continue?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.76,0:17:17.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうしたらいい？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.76,0:17:17.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どう戦ったらいいんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.79,0:17:16.85,default,,0,0,0,,What should I do?\NHow should I fight this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.70,0:17:21.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,行き詰まったカイジ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.70,0:17:21.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,突破口を開く策
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.91,0:17:19.35,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji is now in a dilemma!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.81,0:17:23.35,default,,0,0,0,,Where would he find the solution\Nto lead him to victory?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.50,0:17:27.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝負するための方向性 羅針盤を
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.50,0:17:27.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,彼は必要としていた
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.35,0:17:26.69,default,,0,0,0,,He needs a guide\Nto show him the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.28,0:17:30.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,このままでは あまりにも無策
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.32,0:17:29.95,default,,0,0,0,,At this rate,\Nhe's simply aimless.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.61,0:17:36.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ただ寄る辺なく
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.61,0:17:36.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝負という海原を漂うだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.70,0:17:35.03,default,,0,0,0,,He is just drifting along\Nwith no clue of his direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.22,0:17:38.56,default,,0,0,0,,What is your next bet, Kaiji?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.25,0:17:40.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ君　次のベットは？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.19,0:17:42.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,心のぜい肉…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.29,0:17:42.20,default,,0,0,0,,My foolish pride...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.60,0:17:50.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,２だ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.60,0:17:50.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いいのか 本当に２で？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.62,0:17:46.88,default,,0,0,0,,2.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.39,0:17:49.88,default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure that's your bet?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.03,0:17:54.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝ちゃいいんだろ 勝ちゃ　２だ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.08,0:17:53.38,default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter\Nas long as I win! My bet is 2!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.87,0:17:56.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,とんだ頑固もんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.07,0:17:57.08,default,,0,0,0,,What a stubborn fellow.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.87,0:18:01.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,人が親切心でしている忠告も
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.87,0:18:01.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,素直に聞けんとはな
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.08,0:18:00.89,default,,0,0,0,,To think that you're\Nrefusing my good advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.21,0:18:04.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ふざけるな　その口車に乗って
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.22,0:18:02.44,default,,0,0,0,,Quit messing around!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.48,0:18:07.90,default,,0,0,0,,I'll never heed your words\Nand fall into your trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.95,0:18:08.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これ以上 貴様のペースに
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.95,0:18:08.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,巻き込まれてたまるか
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.75,0:18:12.26,default,,0,0,0,,I will make my own decisions.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.79,0:18:12.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,自分の心の主導権は自分で持つ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.52,0:18:16.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なら２だ　意地を張ってでも
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.57,0:18:15.96,default,,0,0,0,,That's why I'll bet 2,\Neven if it's out of pride!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.73,0:18:20.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,５戦目
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.73,0:18:20.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,皇帝の利根川がカードを選択
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.82,0:18:20.54,default,,0,0,0,,For the fifth game,\NTonegawa chooses his card first.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.60,0:18:24.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして繰り返される同じ思考
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.60,0:18:24.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,同じ理論
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.72,0:18:24.55,default,,0,0,0,,It's the same strategy\Nand mentality.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.77,0:18:29.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,皇帝側では 先出しの１枚で
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.77,0:18:29.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まず勝負には来ない
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.90,0:18:28.80,default,,0,0,0,,The Emperor won't be\Nplaced as the first card.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.17,0:18:32.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なら 市民
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.28,0:18:30.85,default,,0,0,0,,It has to be a Citizen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.08,0:18:34.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,待てよ　ヤツはさっきの勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.20,0:18:34.73,default,,0,0,0,,Wait. In the last match,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.64,0:18:37.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,絶対 来ると思った２枚目で
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.64,0:18:37.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,皇帝を出さなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.73,0:18:37.78,default,,0,0,0,,he didn't deal Emperor for the\Nsecond card as I expected him to.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.98,0:18:39.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,てことは…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.02,0:18:39.09,default,,0,0,0,,In other words...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.92,0:18:42.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１度 考え出すと止まらない疑念
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.06,0:18:42.78,default,,0,0,0,,On starting to ponder,\Nthe indecisiveness begins.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.89,0:18:47.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それは瞬く間に広がり
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.89,0:18:47.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,思考を迷走に導く
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.06,0:18:47.60,default,,0,0,0,,It leads to a labyrinth which\None may never escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.56,0:18:53.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジの心には今 重りがない
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.80,0:18:53.80,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji's mind is\Nunstable right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.96,0:18:57.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝つための思考を組み立てる
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.96,0:18:57.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,足がかり
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.02,0:18:56.74,default,,0,0,0,,He has no clue of any\Nstrategy that would...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.00,0:19:00.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そこに勝負を委ねる
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.00,0:19:00.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,くさびのようなものがなく
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.23,0:19:00.97,default,,0,0,0,,...help him to win\Nthis psychological battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.77,0:19:04.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ゆえに堂々巡りを繰り返す
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.97,0:19:03.75,default,,0,0,0,,And so he finds himself\Nin a precarious position...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.01,0:19:08.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,無重力の空間を漂うように
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.01,0:19:08.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,頼りなく
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.08,0:19:08.25,default,,0,0,0,,...with his mind\Nwandering aimlessly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.85,0:19:11.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,奴隷か
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.99,0:19:10.15,default,,0,0,0,,Slave?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.75,0:19:14.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや 出せねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.79,0:19:13.36,default,,0,0,0,,No, I can't deal this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.39,0:19:19.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,オープン
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.46,0:19:18.57,default,,0,0,0,,Open!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.13,0:19:27.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,面白かろう
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.23,0:19:26.75,default,,0,0,0,,Isn't this interesting?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.76,0:19:29.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今までにあったかね？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.83,0:19:32.04,default,,0,0,0,,Have you\Nexperienced this before?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.70,0:19:35.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これほど必死に人の心を…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.70,0:19:35.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,真実を知ろうとしたことが
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.20,0:19:34.58,default,,0,0,0,,Wanting to know\Nthe truth, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.17,0:19:38.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これが本当の会話だ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.26,0:19:37.32,default,,0,0,0,,This is a conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.41,0:19:40.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,本当の会話？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.46,0:19:40.32,default,,0,0,0,,Conversation?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.41,0:19:42.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そう　このＥカードは
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.65,0:19:42.70,default,,0,0,0,,Right. E-Card is a game...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.68,0:19:47.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,相手の心理 真実の心を
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.68,0:19:47.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,突き止めるゲーム
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.70,0:19:48.39,default,,0,0,0,,...to ascertain the opponent's\Nmind and his real intentions.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.12,0:19:49.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,混じりっけなし
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.15,0:19:52.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,心と心の会話だ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.37,0:19:51.62,default,,0,0,0,,A heart-to-heart conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.89,0:19:56.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この会話の純粋さに比べれば
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.96,0:19:58.74,default,,0,0,0,,Compared to this, your daily\Nconversations with friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.23,0:19:59.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,日常 友人との会話など
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.10,0:20:02.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それが いかに真剣な
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.10,0:20:02.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,相談事であろうと
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.23,0:20:04.21,default,,0,0,0,,be it a serious discussion\Nor one in private,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.00,0:20:04.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,打ち明け話であろうと
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.63,0:20:08.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,所詮はその場限りの
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.63,0:20:08.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,魂のない会話にすぎん
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.72,0:20:08.62,default,,0,0,0,,are transcient\Nand lack spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.94,0:20:10.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが 今はどうだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.06,0:20:10.58,default,,0,0,0,,But what about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.87,0:20:14.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,君は真剣に
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.87,0:20:14.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私の心を測ろうとしている
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.98,0:20:14.72,default,,0,0,0,,You are trying hard\Nto figure me out,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.58,0:20:16.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,むろん私もだ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.72,0:20:16.28,default,,0,0,0,,and likewise on my part.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.61,0:20:19.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この圧倒的会話の濃度
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.83,0:20:19.14,default,,0,0,0,,The intensity\Nof this conversation...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.05,0:20:21.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,日常では味わえまい
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.14,0:20:20.79,default,,0,0,0,,is not something you\Ncan experience everyday.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.08,0:20:26.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかも聴力を賭けているとなれば
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.08,0:20:26.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,必死にならざるを得ない
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.27,0:20:24.00,default,,0,0,0,,Furthermore, with your hearing\Nas a wager,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.00,0:20:25.80,default,,0,0,0,,you have to beat me\Nno matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.32,0:20:28.80,default,,0,0,0,,Surely this is interesting, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.39,0:20:29.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,面白くないはずがなかろう
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.06,0:20:32.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,震えるほどに味わえる
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.06,0:20:32.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝負の愉悦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.08,0:20:33.80,default,,0,0,0,,Savour my impending victory!\NSmell it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.80,0:20:35.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,醍醐味を
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.03,0:20:37.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,心と心の会話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.06,0:20:37.15,default,,0,0,0,,A heart-to-heart conversation...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.77,0:20:42.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,確かにこのＥカード
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.77,0:20:42.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まったく読めなかった相手の心が
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.85,0:20:41.81,default,,0,0,0,,Indeed. In E-Card,\Nthoughts which are invisible...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.61,0:20:46.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,数秒後 いともあっさり
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.61,0:20:46.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,明らかになる
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.76,0:20:45.48,default,,0,0,0,,...will become apparent.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.32,0:20:48.51,default,,0,0,0,,The hidden thoughts\Nof the opponent...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.34,0:20:48.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,隠されていた相手の本心…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.85,0:20:52.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,真実が 何のカードを
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.85,0:20:52.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,出したかによって見えてくる
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.94,0:20:52.12,default,,0,0,0,,...will be revealed by\Nthe cards that he deals.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.79,0:20:54.46,default,,0,0,0,,Hesitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.05,0:20:57.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ちゅうちょ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.05,0:20:57.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,躊躇　勇気　欲望　恐れ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.81,0:20:55.32,default,,0,0,0,,Courage.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.82,0:20:56.46,default,,0,0,0,,Desire.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.88,0:20:57.87,default,,0,0,0,,Fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.59,0:21:01.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,恐れ？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.60,0:21:00.49,default,,0,0,0,,Fear?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.03,0:21:06.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうだ　｢恐れ｣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.09,0:21:06.31,default,,0,0,0,,I see. It's fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.33,0:21:08.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.75,0:21:07.84,default,,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.24,0:21:12.41,default,,0,0,0,,Like a brilliant flash, an idea\Nflashed through Kaiji's mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.26,0:21:12.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,閃光のように
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.26,0:21:12.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジの脳裏を走り抜けた思考
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.24,0:21:15.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それは勝負に導く光明か
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.41,0:21:15.36,default,,0,0,0,,Is this the light that will\Nlead him to victory?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.14,0:21:19.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それとも破滅へ導く地獄の炎か
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.36,0:21:19.00,default,,0,0,0,,Or a hellfire that will\Nlead him to destruction?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.43,0:22:45.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ほんろう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.43,0:22:45.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,次回｢翻弄｣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.54,0:22:45.56,default,,0,0,0,,Next, Trifled.
